WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.520
Get ready with me while I'll tell you why you should be interested

00:00:03.521 --> 00:00:05.481
about the European Parliament elections

00:00:05.482 --> 00:00:06.921
that happened this year.

00:00:06.922 --> 00:00:10.721
Being an European Union citizen gives you a lot of benefits.

00:00:10.722 --> 00:00:13.641
Last summer I visited so many, uh,

00:00:13.642 --> 00:00:17.881
European Union countries because as an European Union citizen,

00:00:17.882 --> 00:00:21.101
I don't need visa, I have data roaming

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:24.800
and I have train connections to pretty much every country.

00:00:24.801 --> 00:00:26.801
And I love travelling, so I really,

00:00:26.802 --> 00:00:28.561
really love that opportunity.

00:00:28.562 --> 00:00:31.161
And I am from Finland, but right now

00:00:31.162 --> 00:00:35.221
I'm living in Poland for the spring and doing volunteer work.

00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:38.640
And I have this opportunity thanks to European Union.

00:00:38.641 --> 00:00:42.361
All these things related to European Union

00:00:42.362 --> 00:00:46.221
is decided in the European Union Parliament.

00:00:46.240 --> 00:00:48.380
And these are only a little examples.

00:00:48.400 --> 00:00:51.480
There is so much benefits like privacy laws,

00:00:51.481 --> 00:00:55.001
environmental laws, so many things that are decided in the EU

00:00:55.002 --> 00:00:57.721
that affects every EU citizens life.

00:00:57.722 --> 00:01:00.541
And did you know these makeup products I'm using

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:04.920
are also following the laws of European Union?

00:01:04.921 --> 00:01:08.821
They check that all the ingredients are safe.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:13.860
So if you want to have an effect on things that are decided in the EU

00:01:14.080 --> 00:01:17.680
that affect your life, please go vote on June.

00:01:17.681 --> 00:01:22.201
We will be telling you more reasons to vote on this TikTok account.

00:01:22.202 --> 00:01:23.596
Thank you.
